<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>X-39MATRIX  ·  Security Hall of Fame</title>
<meta name="description" content="Researchers who contributed to the security of X-39MATRIX Sovereign Topos Protocol">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    background: #050507;
    color: #C8CFD8;
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Consolas', 'Courier New', monospace;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 0 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .container { max-width: 980px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 0 80px; }
  .header {
    border-left: 4px solid #E63946;
    padding: 20px 30px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(230,57,70,0.08), transparent);
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.6rem;
    color: #E63946;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .subtitle {
    color: #00D9FF;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 20px;
    margin: 30px 0 50px;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #0F141C;
    border: 1px solid #1F2530;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .meta-item {
    flex: 1 1 180px;
  }
  .meta-label {
    color: #7A8290;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .meta-value {
    color: #F5F7FA;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .meta-value.gold { color: #D4AF37; }
  .meta-value.cyan { color: #00D9FF; }
  .meta-value.green { color: #00E676; }
  h2 {
    color: #D4AF37;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin: 40px 0 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1F2530;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
  }
  p { color: #C8CFD8; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .hof-empty {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 30px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F141C, #050507);
    border: 1px dashed #7A8290;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin: 30px 0;
  }
  .hof-empty .icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: #D4AF37;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-family: serif;
  }
  .hof-empty h3 {
    color: #F5F7FA;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .hof-empty .quote {
    color: #D4AF37;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .cta {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    background: #E63946;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .cta:hover {
    background: #FF3D52;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    background: rgba(0,217,255,0.1);
    border: 1px solid #00D9FF;
    color: #00D9FF;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-right: 6px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  code {
    background: #0F141C;
    color: #00E676;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }
  .footer {
    margin-top: 60px;
    padding-top: 30px;
    border-top: 1px solid #1F2530;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #7A8290;
    text-align: center;
  }
  a { color: #00D9FF; text-decoration: none; }
  a:hover { color: #D4AF37; }
  ul { list-style: none; }
  ul li { padding: 8px 0 8px 22px; position: relative; }
  ul li::before {
    content: '▸';
    color: #E63946;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

  <div class="header">
    <h1>Hall of Fame</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">X-39MATRIX  ·  Sovereign Topos Protocol  ·  Security Researchers</div>
  </div>

  <div class="meta">
    <div class="meta-item">
      <div class="meta-label">Inaugurated</div>
      <div class="meta-value gold">2026-06-22</div>
    </div>
    <div class="meta-item">
      <div class="meta-label">Bitcoin Anchor</div>
      <div class="meta-value green">Block #95xxxx (pending)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="meta-item">
      <div class="meta-label">Researchers</div>
      <div class="meta-value cyan">0  ·  Be the first</div>
    </div>
    <div class="meta-item">
      <div class="meta-label">Max Reward</div>
      <div class="meta-value gold">USD 50,000</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
  <p>
    We honor the security researchers who help X-39MATRIX become more sovereign by responsibly
    disclosing vulnerabilities. Every confirmed finding earns:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Public recognition (or anonymized by request) on this page</li>
    <li>A monetary bounty per the severity matrix (USD 100 - USD 50,000)</li>
    <li>A coordinated advisory <strong>anchored in Bitcoin mainnet</strong> via OpenTimestamps —
        the finding becomes part of the permanent historical record</li>
    <li>Optional reference letter for future security positions</li>
    <li>Invitation to a private Telegram/Signal group with the operator and other contributors</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Current Hall of Fame</h2>

  <div class="hof-empty">
    <div class="icon">∅</div>
    <h3>This page is intentionally empty.</h3>
    <p>No confirmed findings yet. The challenge is open.</p>
    <p>Our 11 canisters on ICP mainnet are signing real Bitcoin transactions
       without human keys, under quadruple post-quantum protection. Show us what we missed.</p>
    <p class="quote">
      "The first researcher to find a confirmed Critical vulnerability earns up to USD 50,000
      and a permanent place in Bitcoin's block history."
    </p>
    <a class="cta" href="https://hackenproof.com/programs/x39matrix">
      Open the Bounty Program →
    </a>
  </div>

  <h2>What We Look For</h2>
  <p>
    Vulnerabilities that demonstrate concrete compromise of the protocol's three sovereignty pillars:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Pillar 1 — No human key:</strong> any path to unauthorized signing without consensus of the threshold-ECDSA subnet</li>
    <li><strong>Pillar 2 — Quadruple PQ signature:</strong> any forgery of ML-DSA-87 or SLH-DSA, or bypass making either non-mandatory</li>
    <li><strong>Pillar 3 — Cross-substrate anchor integrity:</strong> any rollback, replay or fork attack across BTC + Arbitrum + Solana</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    Plus: bypass of any of the 7 Sovereign Axioms <code>A1–A7</code>
    (sealed in Bitcoin block <code>#948027</code>), corruption of stable memory,
    successful execution of any of the 10 documented collapse attacks <code>ATK-01 → ATK-10</code>.
  </p>

  <h2>How to Submit</h2>
  <p>Three channels, all equally accepted:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>HackenProof:</strong>
      <a href="https://hackenproof.com/programs/x39matrix">hackenproof.com/programs/x39matrix</a>
    </li>
    <li><strong>Email PGP-encrypted:</strong>
      <code>security@x39matrix.org</code>
      (fingerprint <code>C3E062EB 251A1185 1C0B4FFD 06870F06 55D5BBE8</code>)
    </li>
    <li><strong>GitHub Private Vulnerability Reporting:</strong>
      <a href="https://github.com/x39matrix/x39matrix/security/advisories/new">github.com/x39matrix/x39matrix/security/advisories/new</a>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Anchoring &amp; Verification</h2>
  <p>
    Every Hall of Fame update is sealed in Bitcoin mainnet via OpenTimestamps (.ots), so the
    historical record of contributions is mathematically immutable. The current page hash is
    anchored at <code>BTC block #95xxxx</code> (pending confirmation). To verify:
  </p>
  <p>
    <code>curl -s https://x39matrix.org/hall-of-fame.html | sha256sum</code><br>
    <code>ots verify https://x39matrix.org/hall-of-fame.html.ots</code>
  </p>

  <div class="footer">
    <span class="badge">RFC 9116 SECURITY.TXT</span>
    <span class="badge">CVE COORDINATED DISCLOSURE</span>
    <span class="badge">BITCOIN ANCHORED</span>
    <br><br>
    X-39MATRIX Sovereign Topos Protocol  ·  Made from Sevilla, Andalucia<br>
    <a href="https://x39matrix.org">x39matrix.org</a>  ·
    <a href="https://github.com/x39matrix/x39matrix">github.com/x39matrix/x39matrix</a>  ·
    <a href="https://x39matrix.org/X39MATRIX_BOUNTY_PROGRAM_v1.0.pdf">Bounty Program PDF</a>
    <br><br>
    <em>Document inaugurated 2026-06-22, anchored in Bitcoin mainnet.</em>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
